<br>
Like giants in GD, why even bother with them unless looking for something (heads, toes, faction).  Waaay too many hitpoints.  Same with hill giants, experience is trivial on them, money is great, so depends what you want.<br>
<br>
Its all in picking your area, and picking your mobs.  I have good luck fighting the light blue ones, takes nothing to kill and still get good xp. Kill 3 or 4 then med a while.<br>
