21-22 Ogres in Timb Deep<br>
23-34 Dwarfs in OOT<br>
35-40 Nurga<br>
41-48 Nurga or Overthere<br>
49-53 Seafuries in OOT<br>
54+ Raptors in Timb Deep <br>
58 Raptors still &amp; Brownie Guards<br>
<br>
Mages rock soloing.  You just need to know which pet to use when and what strategy to use each time.<br>
<br>
<br>
