 Simple really, snare the mobs...run away cast CoF...repeat till dead. Be sure to circle the mobs to get them grouped so CoF hits them all.<br>
<br>
On a second note mage and wiz mage great partners easy to kill things and never use one bit of mana other than haveing cast that first pet.  My husband plays a wiz and i play a mage. He has a staff called staff of temperal flux and jboots. the staff is an instant cast that lowers the mobs fire and cold resist by 6, it is easy to get sol temple quest.  Sound pointless? Nope the key is instant cast   click click click equal agro on him. he just runs around clicking on mob keeping agro....i sent pet with /pet taunt off. Sit on my behind and see msg you gain party exp.  easy as cake noone ever gets hit even.  sometimes he snares and sometimes not...depends on his mood i guess. Downside is that pet gets exp but hey its so easy why complain? worked great in ew at uthorks awhile back...td at spirolics later and now in cs.<br>
<br>
Canamini 51 mage <br>
Terris Thule<br>
